data.description: Offered at $399,900!!! Log Home situated on 27.85 acres with gorgeous views of the property from the rocking chair front porch. The home offers 3 bedrooms 2 full baths, wood floors throughout, walk-in closets, large walkout basement, and high-speed internet all within minutes from the Town of Appomattox.
